ğŸŸ¢ NODE.JS / EXPRESS CODING QUESTIONS
9. Create Simple Express Server
const express = require("express");
const app = express();

app.get("/", (req, res) => {
  res.send("Hello World");
});

app.listen(3000);

ğŸ“Œ Asked: Express basics


10. REST API (GET & POST)
app.use(express.json());

app.get("/users", (req, res) => {
  res.json(users);
});

app.post("/users", (req, res) => {
  users.push(req.body);
  res.status(201).json(req.body);
});

ğŸ“Œ Asked: REST methods


11. Middleware Example
